<ab facs="#facs_391_r2l25">an eẅch <expan>geworbe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . nach <expan>auſʒweıſu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> eẅrs brıefs etc das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_391_r2l26"><expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu ıſt wol wıſſend daʒ Nıkel erhart </ab>
